          Next, to show: chop (h::p) = h::p
          Note ~(zerop (h::p))       by zero_poly_lead
          If p = |0|,
             Then lead [h] = h <> #0 by poly_lead_const
              and chop [h] = h       by poly_chop_cons, h <> #0
          If p <> |0|,
